en: A number of muscles in our body generates different movements. Balanced muscle strength would help improve\nexercise performance, pain control, and prevent injury risk. The Miniplus muscle function test measures and\nevaluates the muscle strength balance of our body through 7 kinds of movement tests.
tw: 我們體內的許多肌肉會產生不同的運動。平衡的肌肉力量有助於提高運動表現、控制疼痛並預防受傷風險。 Miniplus肌肉功能測試透過7種運動測試來測量和評估我們身體的肌肉力量平衡。

ko: 종합 점수별 평가 등급 : 100~90점 (Very Good), 89~80점 (Good), 79~70점 (Normal), 69점~ (Bad)\n*평가 항목이 1건이라도 없을 경우, 종합 점수가 반영되지 않습니다.
en: Levels by Overall Score : 100~90 (Very Good), 89 ~ 80 (Good), 79 ~ 70 (Normal), 69 ~ (Bad)\nIf there is a missing data, overall score will not be shown.

en: Provide a balance score by measuring strength difference between left and right side. Unbalanced strength might lead to occur injuries in a higher chance when exercising.
tw: 透過測量左右側的力量差異來提供平衡分數。力量不平衡可能會導致運動時受傷的幾率較高。
